    <title>博客备份</title>
    <url>/posts/71e7dca9.html</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<!-- build time:Sat Apr 25 2020 20:31:02 GMT+0800 (GMT+08:00) --><html><head></head><body><h2 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h2><p>本文简单记录了如何把 hexo 博客备份到 GitHub 的分支上，以及如何恢复博客的过程，仅供日后参考使用。</p><a id="more"></a><h2 id="新建分支"><a href="#新建分支" class="headerlink" title="新建分支"></a>新建分支</h2><p>新建一个名为 hexo 的分支，用于保存博客源码。</p><ol><li>设置 hexo 为默认分支。</li><li>把仓库克隆到本地。</li><li>只保留 <code>.git</code> 文件夹，把其他文件删除。</li><li>把之前博客的源码拷贝过来。</li><li>把主题文件夹的 <code>.git</code> 文件删除，否则备份不了主题。</li><li>修改 <code>.gitignore</code> 文件，把 <code>package-lock.json</code> 的添加进去，否则提交后有警告。</li></ol><p>接下来使用命令备份博客到 hexo 分支</p><div class="highlight-wrap"autocomplete="off" autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" contenteditable="true"data-rel="ARMASM"><figure class="iseeu highlight /armasm"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="symbol">git</span> <span class="keyword">add </span>.</span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">git</span> commit -m <span class="string">"Backup"</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">git</span> <span class="keyword">push </span>origin hexo</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure></div><h2 id="日常使用"><a href="#日常使用" class="headerlink" title="日常使用"></a>日常使用</h2><p>推送博客和备份博客的顺序没有硬性规定，个人习惯先推送再备份。</p><p>推送命令</p><div class="highlight-wrap"autocomplete="off" autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" contenteditable="true"data-rel="PLAIN"><figure class="iseeu highlight /plain"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo g -d</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure></div><p>备份命令</p><div class="highlight-wrap"autocomplete="off" autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" contenteditable="true"data-rel="ARMASM"><figure class="iseeu highlight /armasm"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="symbol">git</span> <span class="keyword">add </span>.</span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">git</span> commit -m <span class="string">"Backup"</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">git</span> <span class="keyword">push </span>origin hexo</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure></div><h2 id="恢复博客"><a href="#恢复博客" class="headerlink" title="恢复博客"></a>恢复博客</h2><h3 id="克隆项目到本地"><a href="#克隆项目到本地" class="headerlink" title="克隆项目到本地"></a>克隆项目到本地</h3><p>输入以下命令把博客的备份文件克隆到本地</p><div class="highlight-wrap"autocomplete="off" autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" contenteditable="true"data-rel="CRMSH"><figure class="iseeu highlight /crmsh"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git <span class="keyword">clone</span> <span class="title">https</span>://github.com/GitHub用户名/GitHub用户名.github.io.git</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure></div><h3 id="恢复博客-1"><a href="#恢复博客-1" class="headerlink" title="恢复博客"></a>恢复博客</h3><p>进入克隆的文件夹，打开 git bash，输入以下命令</p><div class="highlight-wrap"autocomplete="off" autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" contenteditable="true"data-rel="CMAKE"><figure class="iseeu highlight /cmake"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm <span class="keyword">install</span> hexo-cli</span><br><span class="line">npm <span class="keyword">install</span></span><br><span class="line">npm <span class="keyword">install</span> hexo-deployer-git</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure></div><p>然后就可以正常使用博客了。</p><!-- rebuild by neat --></body></html>]]></content>
